s/2747978\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2747978&d=xTo9lt5%2FMO3GrXFnFHQdvBAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=32bcab84\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2747978&h=5782a2a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2747978</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T01:13:35.000Z","msg":"生化危機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a8568ba6d165600854734ebae924e93071f6ae3","tid":1091043,"uid":235021,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T01:14:29.000Z","msg":"大共一統江山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6833a145b84e654894fe400cf3dd79904c10ce2","tid":1091043,"uid":46500,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T01:14:51.000Z","msg":"咁仲唔算宣戰?"},{"pid":"754ba3874e9a1ee2ceb3790b43d15b6e749b7e4a","tid":1091043,"uid":106026,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T01:16:10.000Z","msg":"支那人本身咪就係生物武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3b716f79f4878abda3270ce5911a67aca6378f9","tid":1091043,"uid":6242,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T01:19:52.000Z","msg":"戰機戰艦都係執夜冷然後改裝<br />\n現代軍事科技都未搞好就學人搞未來野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"918532ba07f657ea962acf7cf899b42472653849","tid":1091043,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T01:32:22.000Z","msg":"習帝救地球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25ec403b9da0e07c7ea7813c0891bc2584e33677","tid":1091043,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"754ba3874e9a1ee2ceb3790b43d15b6e749b7e4a","tid":1091043,"uid":106026,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-